question.title: I can't build a Slimefun addon for Minecraft, can't collect dependencies
question.body:
I cloned this forked repo into IntelliJIDEA in a new project and made a few changes here and there, now when I build the jar file, it says:

[ERROR] Could not collect dependencies for project dev.j3fftw:LiteXpansion:jar:AQUAVILLE
[ERROR] Failed to read artifact descriptor for com.github.SlimeFun-Lab:Slimefun4:jar:experimental-SNAPSHOT

Can I kindly ask for someone to tell me what am I doing wrong here?
